-v-d495462d"><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">昵称(+20)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">头像(+20)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">性别(+10)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">生日(+10)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">联系邮箱(+20)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">公司网站(+15)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">微信码(+25)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">商协会(+10)</view><view class="grid-item data-v-d495462d">职业状态(+20)</view></view></view><view class="rule-detail-item data-v-d495462d"><view class="detail-label data-v-d495462d">6. 实名认证（最高50分）</view><view class="detail-desc data-v-d495462d">完成实名认证直接获得 50分。</view></view><view class="data-v-d495462d" style="height:40rpx"></view></view></scroll-view><view class="modal-footer data-v-d495462d"><button class="know-btn data-v-d495462d" bindtap="{{B}}">我知道了</button></view></view></uni-popup><view class="bottom-spacer data-v-d495462d"></view></view>